Package: jyotirmoymanifest
Title: Insert Manifestation and Author Blocks in R Scripts
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jyotirmoy", "Das", email = "jyotirmoy.das@liu.se", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5649-4658"))
Description: 
    Provides an RStudio addin and function to insert a customizable "manifestation block" 
    and author metadata into R scripts. The block includes intention-setting messages, script 
    name, purpose, author information, creation/modification dates, citation instructions, and notes. 
    User defaults can be preloaded from a configuration file to minimize repetition.
